### 新建字典类型
POST {{base_uri}}/sys/dicts
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{$random.uuid}}",
  "name": "{{$random.name.username}}",
  "description": "{{$random.lorem.paragraph}}",
  "disabled": true,
  "visibility": 1,
  "value_regex": "/^[0-9]$/"
}


### 新增字典数据
GET {{base_uri}}/sys/dicts?dc=152
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
